  "description": "Configure Key Performance Indicators (KPIs) for the upcoming performance review cycle by creating five specific records in the system. For the 'Software Engineer' job title, add 'Code Quality and Review Standards', 'On-Time Delivery of Sprint Tasks', and 'Technical Documentation', each with a minimum value of 1 and a maximum value of 100. For the 'HR Manager' job title, add 'Employee Retention Rate' and 'Compliance with Labor Regulations', both with a minimum value of 1 and a maximum value of 100.",
